data.description: A beautiful and well maintained single level home with a large shop on 3.9 acres in Idaho County.  Sweeping views off the large back deck to enjoy the views and wildlife.  30x40 shop with room to park your RV, workshop and attached wood/storage shed.  Circle drive and plenty of room to park all your vehicles and toys.  The home has a great floor plan, new roof and shows pride of ownership throughout. A large master bedroom and bath.  A fenced garden area with room to expand.  All the landscapping work around the home has been done for you! The back deck includes awnings for shade, furniture and propane firepit.  Home inspection completed as well!!
